text.tspan: Is cycling a carbon-friendly thing to do? Emphatically yes!
Powered by biscuits, bananas or breakfast cereal, the bike
is nearly 10 times more carbon-efficient than the most
efficient of petrol cars. Cycling also keeps you healthy,
provided you dont end up under a bus.

text.data-name: ReBicycle upcycles donated second-hand bikes into safe, practical commuter bikes to re-home or loan to people on low incomes. Make cycling for transport, health or fun accessible to more Wellingtonians.
